store all the  logs to cloud by attaching a volume through cloud.

fdisk -l
mkfs.ext4 /dev/xvdf
mkdir -p /var/lib/jenkins
add it in fstab(/dev/xvdf /var/lib/jenkins/ ext4 defaults 0 0
mount /var/lib/jenkins

